<heading>take - Pick up a portable box.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>take NAME</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Picks up a portable box from the current location and adds it to your inventory.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>take Key
  Pick up the Key and add it to your inventory.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>drop, inv, look, move, place</paragraph>
